  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to describe the characteristics, evaluation, management and
      outcomes of acute chest pain, and to provide opportunities for future initiatives to improve
      the emergency care for patients experiencing acute chest pain in China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
